{"tid":272454,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係善忘 又捧番洪瑞珍","createTime":"2017-06-05T23:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T12:56:52.000Z","uid":28802,"like":13,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea4b9e54d8c42b509827a876cacc264a0be9238","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"兩年前食到勁多人食完食物中毒<br />\n上曬報章頭條就個個都話以後唔再食<br />\n到最近呢個幾星期喺ig, facebook又見到<br />\n個個post番曬洪瑞珍又好食又剩<br />\n撚曬狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人真係</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c9e3c5117c0dcb666029b2b1291b4157374ef7","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:49:14.000Z","msg":"好唔好食見人見智 但衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ddd0798b64786848a7254afd47a6fda607dd75","tid":272454,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:55:33.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係咁好食，台中同台北又唔同味！<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢咁多分家，好難知邊家出事"},{"pid":"7bfcdf0979f3d1309fe032c0bcdb437f06a74e31","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實又唔係咁好食，台中同台北又唔同味！<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢咁多分家，好難知邊家出事</blockquote><br />\n衛生咁差 不了<br />\n喺香港果陣成60幾人中招<br />\n唔通全部都買同一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e1372865406e98a0de08ce821bf7e93cbba0a7","tid":272454,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:59:52.000Z","msg":"唔係啲網店喺台灣帶返香港擺太耐先出事咩？"},{"pid":"7d806ee72496441a5d5abc18a0aa18930ad070bc","tid":272454,"uid":45374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係啲網店喺台灣帶返香港擺太耐先出事咩？</blockquote><br />\n我記得似係 香港人真係盲反"},{"pid":"445982383dc4bfa3176f029cb34999cb4029eb40","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係啲網店喺台灣帶返香港擺太耐先出事咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n究竟食「洪瑞珍」為何會中毒?<br />\n<br />\n食物在室溫存放過久，會引致病原體繁殖和產生毒素，市民應避免食用已擺放於室溫數小時的熟食或即食食物。<br />\n<br />\n有媒體引述「洪瑞珍」彰化北斗鎮店表示，店內的產品從未透過代理商或貿易商直接銷往香港、國外，都是消費者直接來店購買帶回，對於消費者買回後是自己食用或轉售，公司無權過問。<br />\n<br />\n業界又表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">「洪瑞珍」三明治是用奶油、火腿等新鮮食材，在室溫25度以下，可以存放12小時。而冰箱冷藏可以保存3日，離開冰箱後，必需在3小時內吃完。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/658822/%E6%8F%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%B4%AA%E7%91%9E%E7%8F%8D%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%89%E6%96%87%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E4%B9%8B%E8%AC%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F658822%2F%25E6%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%258F%258D%25E3%2580%258D%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25AC%258E&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7c3d78da\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/658822/%E6%8F%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%B4%AA%E7%91%9E%E7%8F%8D%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%89%E6%96%87%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E4%B9%8B%E8%AC%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n其實真係唔知貪咩 落街啲麵包鋪咪仲新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4901e00506c8e435d38217f51fe0d0d04ff43c","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係啲網店喺台灣帶返香港擺太耐先出事咩？</blockquote><br />\n我記得似係 香港人真係盲反</blockquote><br />\n擺太耐係其因 <br />\n其實我係針對緊點解之前講到話唔再食<br />\n但過一排又繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c106f914dda17161fca80d696be298c72007cff6","tid":272454,"uid":6267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實又唔係咁好食，台中同台北又唔同味！<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢咁多分家，好難知邊家出事</blockquote><br />\n衛生咁差 不了<br />\n喺香港果陣成60幾人中招<br />\n唔通全部都買同一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關咩事，明明佢地唔建議囉出境外，<br />\n<br />\n係有人代理囉出境，你睇七仔三文治果類，<br />\n<br />\n好似都有建議幾個鐘內食左佢或放雪櫃"},{"pid":"6d2ff1597e1acd4a731b5e5ac4fd2b0e2ee27be7","tid":272454,"uid":77164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:05:21.000Z","msg":"真心好食"},{"pid":"33c99e299d086306e69a0d13f11b0d5d98182b8e","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實又唔係咁好食，台中同台北又唔同味！<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢咁多分家，好難知邊家出事</blockquote><br />\n衛生咁差 不了<br />\n喺香港果陣成60幾人中招<br />\n唔通全部都買同一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關咩事，明明佢地唔建議囉出境外，<br />\n<br />\n係有人代理囉出境，你睇七仔三文治果類，<br />\n<br />\n好似都有建議幾個鐘內食左佢或放雪櫃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbdc8cfb6bc8dcaa76ae14be97f117d457bd5e1","tid":272454,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係啲網店喺台灣帶返香港擺太耐先出事咩？</blockquote><br />\n我記得似係 香港人真係盲反</blockquote><br />\n擺太耐係其因 <br />\n其實我係針對緊點解之前講到話唔再食<br />\n但過一排又繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人不嬲都善忘"},{"pid":"ad2522d17a3366f07450055be4fd24b13395e503","tid":272454,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係啲網店喺台灣帶返香港擺太耐先出事咩？</blockquote><br />\n我記得似係 香港人真係盲反</blockquote><br />\n擺太耐係其因 <br />\n其實我係針對緊點解之前講到話唔再食<br />\n但過一排又繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人不嬲都善忘</blockquote><br />\n呢個其實係我開post嘅原因<br />\n衛生條件好唔好我真係唔知<br />\n但喺果陣屌到同狗屎冇分別<br />\n依家又走去食 做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db62d2e6964a609db6f24b9463558636c1225b30","tid":272454,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"巴打少上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有事果時仲有大把代購"},{"pid":"cf01866a8bb06b4b00bebea0ac48a54234e12cee","tid":272454,"uid":18271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:48:31.000Z","msg":"有紅色資本買老麥之後大把連登仔罷食<br />\n一個星期唔使連登仔又吹奏M記<br />\n不要分得那麼細，大家都係死港燦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1422f24186cf9a9a691945a47a28561266ba613f","tid":272454,"uid":23412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:57:28.000Z","msg":"未食過 但唔覺有咩好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而鍾意食全家7仔果隻<br />\n有fd 洪瑞珍同全家7仔都食過 話冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b52ab3f190f2cc8de3186a1f978becad3104c30","tid":272454,"uid":9708,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"可憐 明明係俾香港整臭個朵 都仲要俾人盲反<br />\n人地台灣幾蚊一件三文治有咁既質素 你就覺得人地黑心食店"},{"pid":"0d6b19121e15e7df35ecb1d18a6c2cc9e3ea14c1","tid":272454,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"人地賣25台幣<br />\n香港賣25港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我食舊熱辣辣餐蛋治仲正啦<br />\n<br />\n食過台北唔知邊間洪瑞珍，好普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65fde19e77f52516bda04bab53cef1861bbe20f","tid":272454,"uid":34164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實又唔係咁好食，台中同台北又唔同味！<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢咁多分家，好難知邊家出事</blockquote><br />\n衛生咁差 不了<br />\n喺香港果陣成60幾人中招<br />\n唔通全部都買同一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><